prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style llama wearing a ridiculously small, colorful party hat and oversized sunglasses, looking slightly smug and unimpressed. The llama is surrounded by a gentle explosion of pastel confetti and a few floating, wobbly birthday balloons. In the center, the text "happy birthday" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, lighthearted watercolor style, with visible artistic brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture, creating a warm and funny 2D design.
